itemLabel: Princess Elizabeth of the United Kingdom
itemDescription: Member of the British Royal Family (1770-1840)

wikipedia_page.main: Princess Elizabeth of the United Kingdom (22 May 1770 – 10 January 1840) was the seventh child and third daughter of King George III and Charlotte of Mecklenburg-Strelitz. After marrying the Landgrave of Hesse-Homburg, Frederick VI, she took permanent residence in Germany as landgravine.
